# Some code editor plugins may not use/respect ignore settings passed to
# Prettier, so we need to explicitly ignore node_modules with this file at all
# possible locations. The repository root alone is not enough, such as when
# working with Yarn workspaces.
**/.yarn
**/bower_components
**/jspm_packages
**/node_modules

# Temporary directories for build and development tools
**/.tmp
**/.sass-cache
**/build
**/dist
